{"tid":1162174,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】遭從後飛腳突襲　「未來戰士」阿諾無大礙","createTime":"2019-05-19T16:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T04:29:36.000Z","uid":47496,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"793ac6388ba74cfcd5a7f982aa046673b8f9bcd5","tid":1162174,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:40:19.000Z","msg":"美國前加州州長阿諾舒華辛力加上周六（18日）在南非出席一個公開活動時，突然被一名男子從後起飛腳猛踢，他失去重心伏向前方，但沒有受傷。涉事男子很快被保安人員制服。<br />\n<br />\n阿諾當時出席一項推廣運動與健身的活動。從片段可見，阿諾將手機交給他人後，一名男子突然高速從後踢向阿諾背後，阿諾仆向前。保安員立即按住施襲者。 <br />\n<br />\n曾經演出著名荷里活電影《未來戰士》（Terminator）的阿諾沒有大礙，事後在社交網Twitter報平安︰「多謝大家關心。不需要擔心。我初時以為被人群推撞，這經常發生。後來我看到影片後知道被人踢。我很高興那個瘋子沒有阻礙我的Snapchat聊天。」 <br />\n<br />\n活動負責人表示，警方事前已知悉該名男子曾作出類似行動，強調阿諾沒有受傷，精神很好。阿諾強調無意控告施襲者，又表示會如期於周日（19日）出席活動。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190519/mobile/bkn-20190519010048605-0519_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190519%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190519010048605-0519_00972_001.html&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ16f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=a1ea2242\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190519/mobile/bkn-20190519010048605-0519_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n希望佢冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05333a58d3b3c53fccb22ba99c4cae6a0e6a111e","tid":1162174,"uid":10903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:21:14.000Z","msg":"咁夠薑攻擊t800<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望個力架未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bab75ccdedbd7ecabac27a8df516334d07ede39","tid":1162174,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"今朝已經見到有兩個類似嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2254532f37903ca26d5a74dc7041507efee61aa","tid":1162174,"uid":167330,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:22:08.000Z","msg":"71歲仲操到咁大隻真係好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後面條友有乜居心，成個飛身踢...踢名人搏存在感？"},{"pid":"09bf40151378cb01b2314bd6fa1e65e256923b7a","tid":1162174,"uid":69120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:22:55.000Z","msg":"沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而踢個條友跌落地仲傷咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214c24c1ef4cf2c76d655544cf82f6adc11cba42","tid":1162174,"uid":167330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"05333a58d3b3c53fccb22ba99c4cae6a0e6a111e","tid":1162174,"uid":10903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:21:14.000Z","msg":"咁夠薑攻擊t800<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望個力架未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:22:59.000Z","msg":"佢喺最新嗰套戲仲升級變做T-1000添<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518f4bc2f124401e5d92e506ee39c655479960fe","tid":1162174,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HBuEY4h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHBuEY4h.png&h=a936b5fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e63c71afc801520262e6cac7b88397dc19fc33a1","tid":1162174,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"214c24c1ef4cf2c76d655544cf82f6adc11cba42","tid":1162174,"uid":167330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"05333a58d3b3c53fccb22ba99c4cae6a0e6a111e","tid":1162174,"uid":10903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:21:14.000Z","msg":"咁夠薑攻擊t800<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望個力架未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:22:59.000Z","msg